            "title": "Bryntum Task Board Intro"
        },
        {
            "id": "block_a2016e10d3e520694a7ca1d3ffe417d9",
            "type": "text-media",
            "modifiers": ["image", "reverse", "added-shadow"],
            "eyebrow": "Feature Set",
            "heading": "All the Right Features",
            "body_html": "<p>The Bryntum Task Board ships with a set of optional features carefully designed to suit your workflow:</p> <ul> <li>Tailor the rendering and styling of cards, columns and swimlanes.</li> <li>Flip features on or off at runtime via a flexible API.</li> <li>Scroll smoothly through <a href=\"/products/taskboard/examples/bigdataset/\">huge datasets</a>.</li> </ul>",
            "body_text": "The Bryntum Task Board ships with a set of optional features carefully designed to suit your workflow: Tailor the rendering and styling of cards, columns and swimlanes. Flip features on or off at runtime via a flexible API. Scroll smoothly through huge datasets .",
            "links": [
                {
                    "text": "All the Right Features",
                    "href": "/products/taskboard/examples/config-panel"
                },
                {
                    "text": "huge datasets",
                    "href": "/products/taskboard/examples/bigdataset/"
                }
            ],
            "ctas": [
                {
