        {
            "id": "block_c57f051d24cd8095d56be8d6b7b4e1d6",
            "type": "text-media",
            "modifiers": ["video-file", "added-shadow"],
            "eyebrow": "Organisation",
            "heading": "Group Tasks Into Swimlanes and Columns",
            "body_html": "<p>On a busy team? Stay on top of tasks by tailoring your Task Board with <a href=\"/products/taskboard/examples/swimlanes/\">swimlanes</a> and any number of columns.</p> <ul> <li><a href=\"/products/taskboard/examples/locked-column/\">Pin an important column</a> in place for fast access.</li> <li>Tuck away lower-priority tasks by collapsing swimlanes and columns.</li> <li><a href=\"/products/taskboard/examples/filtering/\">Filter</a> and <a href=\"/products/taskboard/examples/sorting/\">sort</a> tasks to keep your top priorities in view.</li> </ul>",
            "body_text": "On a busy team? Stay on top of tasks by tailoring your Task Board with swimlanes and any number of columns. Pin an important column in place for fast access. Tuck away lower-priority tasks by collapsing swimlanes and columns. Filter and sort tasks to keep your top priorities in view.",
            "links": [
                {
                    "text": "Group Tasks Into Swimlanes and Columns",
                    "href": "/products/taskboard/examples/swimlanes-content/"
                },
                {
                    "text": "swimlanes",
                    "href": "/products/taskboard/examples/swimlanes/"
                },
                {
