        {
            "id": "block_a6810390858a4124774049b1a0e766c8",
            "type": "text-media",
            "modifiers": ["image", "reverse", "added-shadow"],
            "eyebrow": "Customisation",
            "heading": "Fully Shape Your Component",
            "body_html": "<p>Get creative with the many ways you can style the Task Board:</p> <ul> <li>Pick from <a href=\"/products/taskboard/examples/themes\">five built-in themes</a> or roll your own using CSS variables.</li> <li>Render custom text or markup in cards via the <a href=\"/products/taskboard/docs/#TaskBoard/view/TaskBoardBase#config-taskRenderer\"><code>taskRenderer</code></a> method.</li> <li>Choose which elements appear on each card with <a href=\"/products/taskboard/docs/#TaskBoard/view/mixin/TaskItems#config-bodyItems\"><code>bodyItems</code></a>.</li> <li>Drop in <a href=\"/products/taskboard/examples/task-items\">icons, tags, images and progress bars</a> with ease.</li> </ul>",
            "body_text": "Get creative with the many ways you can style the Task Board: Pick from five built-in themes or roll your own using CSS variables. Render custom text or markup in cards via the taskRenderer method. Choose which elements appear on each card with bodyItems . Drop in icons, tags, images and progress bars with ease.",
            "links": [
                {
                    "text": "Fully Shape Your Component",
                    "href": "/products/taskboard/examples/themes"
                },
                {
                    "text": "five built-in themes",
                    "href": "/products/taskboard/examples/themes"
